# Tailwind UI 组件库
id: tailwind-ui
$schema: solarwire-component-library-v1
description: Tailwind CSS 官方出品，营销风格、渐变色、大留白、现代商业感、CTA 驱动
version: 1.0.0
author: SolarWire
createdAt: 2026-04-24T00:00:00Z
updatedAt: 2026-04-24T00:00:00Z

